# OpenAI Images API credential (REQUIRED).
# Read at tool-call time. Absent, empty, or whitespace-only values produce a
# clear error and no API call is made. Never commit your real key — this file
# is only an example; copy it to .env and fill in your key.
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-api-key-here

# Optional: path to a local style/brand file whose contents are prepended to
# every prompt so generated art stays on-brand.
# STYLE_GUIDE_PATH=style-guide.md

# Optional: register the optional tools (true/1/yes/on to enable).
# ENABLE_EDIT_TOOL=false
# ENABLE_LIST_TOOL=false

# Optional: absolute workspace root. All image writes are confined to this
# directory. Defaults to the process launch directory.
# WORKSPACE_ROOT=
